subject: Arnold Palmer Invitational (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods overtook Justin Rose in the third round of the Arnold Palmer Invitational. Woods, the defending champion, is trying to win his eighth title as a professional at Bay Hill.
